                                                                                                                                Indicators and status

                                                                                                                                Badge

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                Badges are visual indicators that appear for new notifications, numeric counts, or statuses.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics


                                                                                                                                Numeric badges

                                                                                                                                Dot badges

                                                                                                                                Dot inline
                                                                                                                                Dot on icon
                                                                                                                                Dot on shape



                                                                                                                                Type and color

                                                                                                                                Stroke (Optional): Stroke color = Background color

                                                                                                                                Dot outline
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Use background color for dot stroke color to mimic empty space between dot and shape.
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don’t let stroke color show against shape and/or background color

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                Ensure that any icons or concepts represented with a badge are labeled.

                                                                                                                                Hint badge on shape
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Filter, filters applied. Button.”

                                                                                                                                Label: Filter, [badge label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                Here, the dot badge represents that filters have been applied to the results below.

                                                                                                                                Hint badge on icon
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Food tab, new items, One of four tabs, Button."


                                                                                                                                Label: [Tab label] tab, [badge label]

                                                                                                                                Value: [#] of [total # of tabs]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint badge on text
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Promotions, new items. Button.”

                                                                                                                                Label: Promotions, [badge label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Notification badge on text
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Inbox, 2 new messages. Button.”


                                                                                                                                Label: Inbox, [# on badge] [ badge label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button
